    implementation_delta: |-
      CYCLE 36: BUG FIX — Fixed LND validator key regex.
      Issue: Validator rejected valid keys with uppercase letters (LND_SCHEMA_005, E_RT_FUEL_EXHAUSTED).
      Root cause: Regex ^[a-z0-9_]+$ only allowed lowercase.
      Fix: Changed to ^[a-zA-Z0-9_]+$ in scripts/lnd_validate.py.
      Validation results: LND evolution/ PASSED, LND formats/ PASSED, LND contracts/ PASSED.
      Commits: a16995d (validator fix), 78a940b (cycle log update).
